  <summary date="2021-08-23T14:40:15Z" status="Introduced in House">Charitable Conservation Easement Program Integrity Act of 2021

This bill imposes a limitation on the tax deduction for qualified conservation contributions made by certain partnerships if the amount of the contribution exceeds 2.5% times the sum of each partner's relevant basis in the partnership. This limitation also applies to other pass-thru entities, such as S corporations.</summary>
